rows.label: bf02010100_0010
rows.name:
...And so Punin wisely
ran away for dear life.

rows.label: bf02010100_0020
rows.name: Wise? Who wise now?

rows.label: bf02010100_0025
rows.name: You useless idiot.

rows.label: bf02010100_0030
rows.name:
Why can Punin not even die properly?
What if they ask Bahn to repay money, hmm?

rows.label: bf02010100_0040
rows.name: Huh? Die? Repay who?

rows.label: bf02010100_0050
rows.name: Meh! None of your business.

rows.label: bf02010100_0060
rows.name: Anyway. Tell me where Rex and Blade went.

rows.label: bf02010100_0070
rows.name: Rex, Divine Beast and friends ran away!

rows.label: bf02010100_0080
rows.name:
Went to south of Cyclus Sea - after
that, Bahn know as much as Punin!

rows.label: bf02010100_0090
rows.name: Storm was very thick, so Punin...

rows.label: bf02010100_0100
rows.name: Punin lose them, yes?

rows.label: bf02010100_0110
rows.name: Yes, but-

rows.label: bf02010100_0120
rows.name: And then run away like coward?

rows.label: bf02010100_0130
rows.name: Y-yes, but-

rows.label: bf02010100_0140
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh-meh-meh!
Bahn not wanting feeble excuses of Punin!

rows.label: bf02010100_0150
rows.name: Just get back here!

rows.label: bf02010100_0160
rows.name: You got lot of work to do!

rows.label: bf02010100_0170
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh... Even pricey insurance Bahn
take out on Maelstrom go to waste...

rows.label: bf02010100_0180
rows.name: Still, how interesting...

rows.label: bf02010100_0190
rows.name: Heading southward from Cyclus Sea...

rows.label: bf02010100_0200
rows.name:
In current season, that likely
take them to Gula.

rows.label: bf02010100_0210
rows.name: You, girl! Get Consul Morph on the line immediately!

rows.label: bf02010100_0220
rows.name:
Yes, sir.
One moment, please.

rows.label: bf02010100_0230
rows.name:
Why, if it isn't Chairman Bahn.
What an unexpected pleasure.

rows.label: bf02010100_0240
rows.name:
May I just say that I admire how you
rebranded those broken Core Crystals.

rows.label: bf02010100_0250
rows.name:
And selling them on to the dunderheads
back in Superbia - absolutely sublime!

rows.label: bf02010100_0260
rows.name: Bahn did not call to hear pointless flattery!

rows.label: bf02010100_0270
rows.name:
And blabbering about Core Crystals on
unsecured line?! Is Morph some kind of idiot?

rows.label: bf02010100_0280
rows.name: What if Acedia tap our communication?

rows.label: bf02010100_0290
rows.name:
O-oh, of course!
I'm very sorry!

rows.label: bf02010100_0300
rows.name:
Meh, forget it.
We got bigger fishies to fry.

rows.label: bf02010100_0310
rows.name: Oh? What's going on?

rows.label: bf02010100_0320
rows.name: Listen up...
